reviewText: You've got to be kidding. I ran across this on a streaming Roku channel. Unbelievably piss poor production values. I don't even know why this stuff exists. Is there a market for it?

NYOKA IS STRONG, CAPABLE--AND OH SO VOLUPTUOUS! SHE'S LIKE A FEMALE INDIANA JONES! THE CRIMSON SKULL IS CREEPY, SADISTIC AND YOUR WORST NIGHTMARE! THIS FEATURE-LENGTH ADVENTURE IS OH SO ENTERTAINING WITH A MAD GORILLA STALKING THE STEAMY JUNGLES AS WELL! SURE TO BECOME A CULT-STATUS CLASSIC.
